## 01. WHAT PFTE IS

**Three-layer definition. All three must be present in every release.**

### Layer 1 — Science
Every PFTE release is grounded in legitimate audio/sonic research.
Frequency science, brainwave entrainment, psychoacoustics, sleep architecture, cognitive performance research.
The science determines the functional architecture of the audio — frequencies used, phase structure, duration, technical specifications.

This is not decoration. This is the foundation.

### Layer 2 — Brand DNA
PFTE has a defined aesthetic identity: pharmaceutical-brutalist.
Clinical. Architectural. Minimal. Dark palette. IKB and black.
Named phase protocols (001 SIGNAL / 002 INDUCTION / etc.)
Every release follows the same structural language.

This is what separates PFTE from generic ambient/utility channels.

### Layer 3 — Bill's Taste
Personal aesthetic injection into the production direction.
Electronic. Psychedelic where appropriate. Textured. Not pretty for pretty's sake.
The science and the brand DNA are the frame. The taste is what makes it listenable and distinctive.

**The formula:**
`Science base + PFTE brand architecture + personal taste = the product`

