## 04. RELEASE ARCHITECTURE STANDARDS

Every PFTE release must include:

**Audio:**
- Mastering: −14 LUFS (Spotify/EBU R128) — except sleep at −20 LUFS
- True peak: ≤ −1 dBTP
- Tool: Shutter Encoder, EBU R128
- Duration: minimum 2 hours. 3 hours standard. Extended versions where appropriate.
- Phase structure: named protocol baked into track titles

**Metadata / YouTube:**
- Title formula: `[Outcome] | [Audio Type] | [Audience / Use Case]`
- Description: science rationale explicitly stated — 2-3 sentences citing research basis
- Phase architecture listed
- AI content disclosure included

**Visual:**
- Pharmaceutical-brutalist identity
- IKB / black / dark palette
- No generic nature or spa visual language
- Consistent with PFTE brand system

